<inglise> (a) professional activities of persons who, acting with complete freedom as to their choice of undertaking, bring together, with a view to the insurance or reinsurance of risks, persons seeking insurance or reinsurance and insurance or reinsurance undertakings, carry out work preparatory to the conclusion of contracts of insurance or reinsurance and, where appropriate, assist in the administration and performance of such contracts, in particular in the event of a claim; </inglise>
<eesti> a) isikute ametialane tegevus, kes ettev&otilde;tja valimise t&auml;ieliku vabaduse tingimustes koondavad riskide kindlustamiseks v&otilde;i edasikindlustamiseks kindlustust v&otilde;i edasikindlustust soovivad isikud ja kindlustusseltsid v&otilde;i edasikindlustusseltsid, tegelevad kindlustuslepingute v&otilde;i edasikindlustuslepingute s&otilde;lmimiseks vajalike eelt&ouml;&ouml;dega ja aitavad vajaduse korral selliste lepingute haldamisel ja t&auml;itmisel eelk&otilde;ige siis, kui tegemist on n&otilde;uetega; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) professional activities of persons instructed under one or more contracts or empowered to act in the name and on behalf of, or solely on behalf of, one or more insurance undertakings in introducing, proposing and carrying out work preparatory to the conclusion of, or in concluding, contracts of insurance, or in assisting in the administration and performance of such contracts, in particular in the event of a claim; </inglise>
<eesti> b) isikute ametialane tegevus, kellele on &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitme lepinguga antud juhised v&otilde;i volitused tegutseda &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitme kindlustusseltsi nimel ja huvides v&otilde;i ainult nende huvides seoses kindlustuslepingute tutvustamise, lepingu s&otilde;lmimise ettepaneku tegemise, lepingu s&otilde;lmimisele eelneva t&ouml;&ouml;ga tegelemisega v&otilde;i kindlustuslepingute s&otilde;lmimisega v&otilde;i selliste lepingute haldamisele v&otilde;i t&auml;itmisele kaasaaitamisega eelk&otilde;ige siis, kui tegemist on n&otilde;udega; </eesti>
