<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The pursuit for at least one year of one of the activities referred to in Article 2 (1) (a) or (b) and receipt of the relevant training shall be regarded as satisfying the requirements laid down in paragraph 1. </inglise>
